instalation mongodb:
1. edit php.ini 
extension=php_mongodb.dll
2. put php_mongodb.dll (version 1.2.0) to php/ext
3. use composer (from php project root directory):
composer require mongodb/mongodb
4. put php_mongodb.dll (version newest) to php/ext


# php location: /usr/local/bin/php7-cli
#/usr/local/bin/php7-cli -r "copy('https://getcomposer.org/installer', 'composer-setup.php');"
#/usr/local/bin/php7-cli composer-setup.php
#/usr/local/bin/php7-cli composer.phar uninstall  catfan/Medoo
#/usr/local/bin/php7-cli composer.phar require  catfan/Medoo
#/usr/local/bin/php7-cli composer.phar update


#to add new required lib in composer
1. add package to composer.json
2. cd public_html/cesspool/
3. /usr/local/bin/php7-cli composer.phar update